<ul>
    <li>Record-breaking attendance numbers at the venue (Jewish Museum) with over 400 visitors during the event.</li>

    <li>Developed new relationships with local Camden based schools, reaching over 120 young people directly.</li>

    <li>Curated the Jewish Museum's first ever exhibition of art created by children.</li>
</ul>

